'''线粒体拟核相关蛋白'''（{{lang-en|mitochondrial nucleoid-associated protein}}）是存在于[[线粒体拟核|线粒体拟核]]中的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]的统称，主要包括[[转录因子|转录因子]]、[[单链DNA结合蛋白|单链DNA结合蛋白]]以及众多参与[[线粒体|线粒体]]中[[代谢途径|代谢途径]]的多功能蛋白。这些蛋白质均由[[核基因|核基因]]编码, 在[[细胞质基质|细胞质基质]]中[[蛋白质生物合成|合成]]再转运至[[线粒体基质|线粒体基质]]内执行功能。<ref>{{cite journal
 |author   = Ryan MT, Hoogenraad NJ
 |title    = Mitochondrial-nuclear communications
 |journal  = Annual Review of Biochemistry
 |volume   = 76
 |issue    = 
 |pages    = 701-702
 |pmid     = 17227225
 |doi      = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.76.052305.091720
 |url      = http://coecxs.org/downloads/Publications/2007/44.%20Mitochondrial-nuclear%20communications%20(Ryan).pdf
 |language = en
 |date     = Jul 2007
}}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>除了参与[[转录|转录]]，线粒体拟核相关蛋白在[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]（mtDNA）折叠和线粒体拟核结构组织中也发挥重要作用。线粒体拟核的结构与功能的完整性都依赖于这些蛋白之间以及蛋白与mtDNA间的[[相互作用|相互作用]]。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Chen XJ, Butow RA
 | title = The organization and inheritance of the mitochondrial genome
 | journal = Nature Reviews Genetics
 | volume = 6
 | issue = 11
 | pages = 815-825
 | pmid = 16304597
 | doi = 10.1038/nrg1708
 | url = http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v6/n11/abs/nrg1708.html
 | language = en |date=Nov 2005}}</ref>多种线粒体拟核相关蛋白的缺失也会使拟核结构不稳定，并最终导致[[DNA损伤|DNA损伤]]。


== 历史 ==
1974年研究人员用[[氨银染色法|氨银染色法]]在[[多头绒泡菌|多头绒泡菌]]（''Physarum polycephalum''）线粒体中观察到了完整的拟核结构。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = T. Kuroiwa and M. Hizume
 | title = Mitochondrial nucleoid staining with ammoniacal silver
 | journal = 
 | volume = 87
 | issue = 2
 | pages = 406-409
 | pmid = 4137845
 | doi = 10.1016/0014-4827(74)90504-7
 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0014482774905047
 | language = en |date=Aug 1974}}</ref>随后，在1976年人们成功将其从线粒体中分离出来，并利用[[SDS-聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳|SDS-聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳]]证实线粒体拟核中含有蛋白质。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = T. Kuroiwa, S. Kawano and M. Hizume
 | title = A method of isolation of mitochondrial nucleoid of Physarum polycephalum and evidence for the presence of a basic protein
 | journal = Experimental Cell Research
 | volume = 97
 | issue = 2
 | pages = 435-440
 | pmid = 942924
 | doi = 10.1016/0014-4827(76)90638-8
 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0014482776906388
 | language = en |date=Feb 1976}}</ref>

